snippet.textDisplay:
U have ozil build the team around him and give him the freedom
To enjoy his football
And he will run himself
Into the ground for arsenal.
That is the difference between coaches and managers. A manager
Gets the best out of every player. That’s his aim. A coach sends a team out to play to a game plan.
It may seem that they both have the same intentions but when u have a brilliant thinker like ozil in ur team and u don’t use him in that pocket position u either have something personal against him or u r an absolute moron.
Let’s ask every striker in the pl who they would like as as their supply source I think u would be shocked that the majority would pick ozil.
Because every striker looks for that one opportunity to score .he may make 30 runs in a match but it’s that one difence splitting pass that leads to a scoring opportunity that counts.
U can defend like Trojans it’s irrelevant if u don’t score.
Let’s not forget football is entertainment and ozil is an entertainer.
Well done arterta for
Letting the players be the focal point .
Unlike some others who think the manager is the focal point.
Keep going young man we are with u .

snippet.textDisplay:
EL is definitely still our only chance of clawing back into CL. I believe there are still Quality issues, and that we probably will sadly fall at a late hurdle again, looking at the board's spending nous.
But if they could just part with Mustafi and land Upemancano, our chance goes up greatly. With the current group? Nah. Ozil still offers 0 goals from CM, a position we desperately need a player to score if Auba / Pepe have off days (and they certainly have)
